REFERRED TO INVESTIGATIONS AND GOVERNMENT OPERATIONS
AMEND (T) AND RECOMMIT TO INVESTIGATIONS AND GOVERNMENT OPERATIONS

Title: Prohibits certain fees from being imposed by licensed wholesalers
Summary: Prohibits certain fees from being imposed by licensed wholesalers on licensed retailers.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the alcoholic beverage control law, in relation to prohibited fees
